title: Fendi First Small Shoulder Bag
description: Fendi First small shoulder bag in light brown Nappa leather. Featuring gold-toned hardware, an oversized metal F-shaped clasp with leather bands, and detachable and adjustable shoulder strap. The top opens to a brown interior lined with the Fendi FF fabric jacquard motif. Approximate dimensions: 24cm(Base-L) x 17cm(H) x 9cm(D), strap drop 48cm. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
